{"tid":1541033,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪應該要六月以降既示威改返個名","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T15:43:02.000Z","uid":105924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"57d4922710aa5e6a487deeb3d8dddd81a1d976ff","tid":1541033,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:21:11.000Z","msg":"林鄭宣佈撤回逃犯修訂條例之後，好多外國人都話係victory，我諗係因為大家都未有幫呢三個月以黎既示威改名，我見好多外國傳媒都係叫protests against the extradition bill之類，令到外國人有個錯覺以為我地剩係爭取撤回逃犯修訂條例，所以係咪應該要好似雨傘革命同魚蛋革命咁幫呢場示威改返個名去legitimize返林鄭宣佈撤回條例後爭取其餘四大訴求既示威？<br />\n咁樣做其實可以防止到林鄭用「示威者偏離原先對條例既訴求」做藉口黎合理化警隊鎮壓示威者，第二係令外國政府更加容易係林鄭宣佈撤回條例繼續為香港人發聲"},{"pid":"07c3be3a86e5e1ec8d0051711e0ad05bd14adcea","tid":1541033,"uid":264717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRLkgWV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRLkgWV.jpg&h=16fc2fc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dCOU5Qf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdCOU5Qf.jpg&h=76e1a51d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b62ba8cfcea5a3a08d06e69e0a26415f9c5732d","tid":1541033,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:22:07.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"4e1fb861460cd3de92cd3f52e44abf8c62cb1939","tid":1541033,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:22:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c5a2a14a07e273d2486a3458e3ae76090b5bc5d","tid":1541033,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:22:45.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"f8c07593db969ac9dcfea50673e47d2711a25cb0","tid":1541033,"uid":231759,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:23:00.000Z","msg":"water revolution"},{"pid":"86c5c2df7417e449d275031e8ef7b4f000b3eb15","tid":1541033,"uid":105924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img sr